values:
So, I'm changing journals. <lj user="breakthehabit"> is my new home.
I'm adding those of you who I've had on my list for a while. If I didn't add you, don't take it personally, it's probably because I don't think you read my journal. Go ahead and add me if you'd still like to be on my list.
Yes. I decided to start over once again. I'll always feel a need to make changes as long as I continue to make mistakes. . . . . Friends only. I'll most likely add you if I see you've added me.
